  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 11th level, you gain the ability to channel your ki into searing waves of energy. Your Sun Soul Bolt attacks that are part of your Attack action can instead damage all creatures in an area in front of you for 1 ki per burst. Each creature in a cone of a size equal to your walking speed must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes your Sun Soul Bolt damage plus your Wisdom modifier (minimum of 1) on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>If you attempt to Stunning Strike through the burst of energy, you must expend one use of the feature per creature.</p>",
